Hebrew Python
=============

First release. Implementation based on idea by Noam Raphael.

To write Hebrew scripts, see hpy/hebrew.py and the example scripts.

Changes
=======

0.1.1 2005-08-28
----------------

- Fix indentation bug
- Mangle only non-ascii identifiers - this allows any standard python in hebrew python script
- Add mix script using standard and hebrew python
- Rename factorial the Hebrew name
- Rename lambda keyword
- Extract method source(path) from execute(path) (kobi zamir)


0.1 2006-08-27
--------------

Initial release.